who should install bigfix stanford answers stanford university stanford answers who should install bigfix categories accounts and ids administrative applications anti virus and security computer operating systems connecting to the network desktop hardware and support email and calendar help desk restricted information on it services software at stanford stanford hospital and clinics telephones and cable tv unix systems and software web services user login login with your sunet id home who should install bigfix search this site all stanford faculty staff and students are entitled to and should install the bigfix client software on any personally owned or stanford owned laptop or desktop computers that are connected to the stanford network or that are used to transact university business even if the isp internet service provider is not stanford bigfix is available for all current versions of microsoft windows and for macintosh os x you can download either version from the essential stanford software site if you have local technical support talk to your support staff before installing the bigfix client in many cases it will be they who have first contacted you requesting that you install the software or bigfix may have been installed on your computer when you first took possession of it if you have questions regarding the installation of bigfix that are not addressed by available documentation please submit a helpsu request bigfix works cooperatively with other automated update services like windows automatic updates and you are encouraged to install bigfix even if you are already updating your computer by other means bigfix stanford university 450 serra mall stanford california 94305 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints
